com.opengamma.strata.basics.date

Class AdjustableDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.basics.date.AdjustableDate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class AdjustableDate
extends Object
implements ImmutableBean, Serializable
    An adjustable date.

    This class combines an unadjusted date and the business day adjustment necessary to adjust it. Calling the adjusted() method will return the adjusted date.

    Usage

    AdjustableDate contains enough information to directly return the adjusted date: 
      LocalDate adjusted = adjustableDate.adjusted();
